title: Interpretation of seeing a crocodile in a dream by Ibn Sirin and Al-Nabulsi

preview.html: I likeFansSubscribersFansInterpretation of seeing a crocodile in a dream by Ibn Sirin and Al-Nabulsi. The crocodile is one of the animals that many people dream about, but the crocodile usually gives them very bad impressions in the dream, but this is not true at all because there are interpretations of the crocodile immediately and others are expected, and to learn more about Interpretation of seeing a crocodile in a dream. Interpretation of a crocodile in a dream according to Nabul: Whoever sees a crocodile dragging him into the water and killing him means that God knows that the sleeper will be subjected to murder and violence by the police or strong authorities in power. As for whoever sees that the crocodile has hit him and touched him, whether on the head or in the Skinning him, this means that he will obtain money from his enemy. As for those who see this, the crocodile crawling down means the sleeper’s victory over his enemy until he took the enemy’s money, and God knows best. Interpretation of a dream about escaping from a crocodile. If the sleeper dreams that he is escaping from a crocodile, this means that the sleeper has great fears in his life. And he is afraid to confront it or approach it. Interpretation of swimming with a crocodile in a dream If you dream that you are swimming in the water with a crocodile, this means that God knows that you need feelings, tenderness, confinement, and perhaps a message to start searching for a wife if you are not married. Interpretation of a crocodile bite in a dream If you dreamed that a crocodile It bites you in a dream, it means that you are ignoring many important issues in your life or you need to stop at these issues, deal with them, solve them and get rid of them. See a crocodile in the garden If you dream of seeing a captive crocodile in a park, dream that the sleeper has a very large number of talents and is gifted with God is the Most High, Blessed, and He must search for it well, develop it, and benefit from it. Of these.Interpretation of killing a crocodile in a dream: If you are a crocodile lover, this means that there is no indication of the presence of great strength in life, and others, which indicates the presence of an important point in the future. Period. Interpretation of seeing a crocodile in a dream for a single woman. If an unmarried woman sees a crocodile in a dream, this means that she is complaining about injustice and that there is someone who is oppressing and persecuting her and trying to escape from it. As for whoever sees the crocodile while it is completely calm and does not move, then the interpretation of the dream and God knows that the sleeper will be exposed For a very large conspiracy by one of the people who are completely close to him. But if the sleeper dreams that there is a group of crocodiles looking at him, but they do not approach him, in the interpretation of the dream, God knows that there are those who conspire against evil and plot against him. We told you a number of interpretations for seeing a crocodile in A dream according to many scholars and in some cases.

title: Interpretation of identity, vision of identity in a dream

preview.html: Identity cardInterpretation of a dream about identitySeeing the loss of identity in a dreamInterpretation of a status card in a dreamCard in a dreamLoss of identityInterpretation of a dream about losing a status cardIdentity theft in a dreamLoss of identity in a dreamGetting a new identity in a dreamThe identity card or identity card in a dream is the official identifier of a person and thus records all his details and information, starting from name, address, date of birth to profession, social status, psychological and physical level. If you dream that you are going to a security area or police station to get your identity card, this is a positive sign related to work, travel, employment and perhaps marriage. Obtaining identity in a dreamIf you dream that you are receiving your identity card from the security services or police, this is an interpretation that you are entering an important and meaningful stage in your life. If the identity card is new, healthy and confidential and the data recorded on it is correct, this should be interpreted as the correctness of the decisions made or the actions taken and related to the future. If the issuance or receipt of the ID card is delayed, this indicates some obstacles that the fortune teller's path or endeavors may face in the current period. A torn and worn ID card or ID card in a dream. A torn or torn national ID card in a dream expresses a person's problems, fears, or dissatisfaction with accepting his current situation and status and his refusal to submit or surrender to his harsh conditions. Interpretation of the personal photo attached to the ID in a dream. If the personal photo attached to the card is healthy and beautiful, it expresses a general stable state on the psychological, social and economic levels, but the torn or ugly photo, in reality, expresses a difficult situation and accumulated problems or a deep crisis that exhausts the viewer or leads to multiple crises. Loss of identity and difficulty finding in a dream. As for the loss of identity, it is evidence of fear of the future, or rather fear of the unknown and failure. The person who always sees himself losing his identity or identity in a dream may be a person who does not trust those around him very much and therefore fears falling into their traps or nefarious plans that aim to destroy him morally through conspiracies or fallacies about the priest to put him in a bad light in front of people. Do not forget that the identity card or national number contains the most important data, and therefore its loss or loss is a symbol of disclosing personal secrets.
